 game is from the Horror-Narrative genre, designed for horror movie lovers.<br></strong></li><li><strong>Orientation:</strong> In a forest and without a compass, the most difficult thing is to find your way around, make it on your own, your family is waiting for you.<br></li><li><strong>No saving:</strong> This game is made to be passed in the same game, due to its simplicity, but it will not be an easy task.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/2.gif?t=1728531093\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/kana.png?t=1728531093\" /><br><br>Our studio specializes in scary games, and we often use Japanese folklore and mythology as a source of inspiration.<br>At Kanashi Studio we study the price, and we set an affordable one for all players, &quot;giving is receiving&quot;.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/icon.png?t=1728531093\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The movie starts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2267930/bbf1cebf634614d98f945f6ff8561d508e276441.jpg"},{"name":"First scare","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2267930/d2d970053259568379e07e711f83e9ef58fe17ee.jpg"},{"name":"Buh!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2267930/58bf342ead80955326a41d5b90d2e850d7ac2b3a.jpg"},{"name":"A kappa","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2267930/1b2c895e79cdb912312e996f2a9218cf5a88becd.jpg"},{"name":"Is this an end?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2267930/2dd2c33c300e5ecb551b68725eae0331a0637297.jpg"},{"name":" Lost in the woods","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/226